{"tid":759585,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"尖沙咀港鐵站大堂有支那蝗童當眾便溺　職員派人清理","createTime":"2018-07-28T17:47:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-28T19:18:31.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"917cc966bbccbc3e2a7b62f06fb778874b680df0","tid":759585,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T17:47:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1409414_1_L_20180728204258.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1409414_1_L_20180728204258.jpg&h=6c79e7dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1409414-20180728.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1409414-20180728.htm&d=%2FRiP%2BKE061bgsUjN78l9zwHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=dcc94b03\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1409414-20180728.htm&h=dddf928d\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1409414-20180728.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n有支那蝗童下午在尖沙咀港鐵站便溺，港鐵職員到場勸止，以及派清潔🇨🇳🇨🇳人員🇨🇳🇨🇳清理。<br />\n<br />\n根據社交平台上的片段所見，有支那蝗童懷疑於港鐵站大堂的角落便溺，同行的有幾個身穿同款藍色上衣和戴帽的男童以及一個男子。他當時以🇨🇳🇨🇳普通話🇨🇳🇨🇳回應拍片者，指涉事支那蝗童當時肚子不適。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵表示，尖沙咀客務中心職員下午一時半接獲乘客報告，職員到場勸止支那蝗童，並安排清潔🇨🇳🇨🇳人員🇨🇳🇨🇳清理，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">有關人士之後離開車站</span></span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n港鐵表示，現時部分車站設有公共洗手間供乘客使用，至於無洗手間的車站，乘客有需要可聯絡職員借用。"},{"pid":"38ef124c7efbcb0ba3de59def1d3b753e5588047","tid":759585,"uid":90660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T19:18:31.000Z","msg":"即刻扣15分 永遠驅逐出境<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}